  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The creature inside claws at the egg with tiny hands.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for an aggressive nature, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">ferociously</span> protective of its Traveller companion.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个有生命的、可生育的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>里面的生物正用小小的手指刮挠着蛋壳。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有好斗的基因潜质，并且会<span class=\"name name-fuel\">凶猛</span>保护自己的旅行者同伴。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>這隻生物在裡面不斷用小爪子抓著蛋殼。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：激烈性情，會<span class=\"name name-fuel\">凶猛地</span>保護自己的旅行者同伴。"
  },
